{
  "stem": "521.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was marching from [NON-ENGLISH] from Koszeg right up to Mauthausen, and from Mauthausen, we were walking to Gunskirchen.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now Gunskirchen, we were walking in rain.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think it must have been two solid days of rain, day and night.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were in the water, but, again, my sleeping bag was waterproof.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was saved by this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now when we went to sleep, we were sleeping in such a manner that we were touching each other.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Like it was maybe 20 or 30 people who were lying side by side in order to keep warm.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Of course, you didn't keep warm, but it was still some kind of protection, except for the first and the last person.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now in the evening, if you had to get up, then by the time you came back, you didn't have your spot anymore.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This was one of the first things what happened to day and night.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "By that time, the people were so sick and tired of living that I remember there was one man who was sitting on a kind of a milestone.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was a kilometer stone, but it didn't mean-- it was a stone.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we were supposed to get up and go, and the German man said to him, now get up and go.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he didn't even bother to answer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So he said, if you don't get up and go, I am going to shoot you.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He didn't say a word.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He got out his revolver and shot him right there in the head.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We were so dehumanized, like, I and the rest of them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So we didn't really mind what is going to happen to us or to anybody else.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We were absolutely senseless.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "There was no impression on us.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
